@node intro "Introduction"

 What is it for?

       Check user new public and  waiting mail (Dlglogin.batch).
       ATTENTION! You need KickStart 2.04 or higher.

@endnode

@node using "Using"

   Put this in Login.dlgbatch file:
 
   Dlg:DiaMail

@endnode

@node display "Display"

                            ---

   Checking for new public messages addressed to you...     
   Area:   5   Msg: 145   Fm:Janne Saarme           Sj: Hello
   Area:   12  Msg: 43    Fm:Ville Saari            Sj: Thanks
                                                         
   These messages have been tagged.                         
 
   Checking for new private messages addressed to you..                            
               Msg: 5     Fm: SkyFreq v3.11          Sj: File-Request of 1:2702/1.0
                                                                                
   Do you want to delete your waitingmail.data (y/N)?                                                        

                            ---

Area = Message area, Msg = Message number, Fm = From, Sj = Subject.

@endnode

